\begin_layout Standard
The GPR model, first introduced in 
\begin_inset CommandInset citation
LatexCommand cite
key "Peshkov2016"

\end_inset

, has its roots in Godunov and Romenski's 1970s model of elastoplastic deformati
on (see 
\begin_inset CommandInset citation
LatexCommand citet
key "godunov2003elements"

\end_inset

).
 It was expanded upon in 
\begin_inset CommandInset citation
LatexCommand citet
key "Dumbser2016a"

\end_inset

 to include thermal conduction.
 This expanded model takes the following form:
\end_layout

